        <mj-text color="#004769" font-size="20px" font-weight="700" align="left">Learn how to meet your clients’ responsible investing goals</mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#000"  font-size="18px" font-weight="400" align="left">
          With the explosion of ESG and RI investment offerings, you may be justifiably
          overwhelmed when it comes to choosing the product that suits your clients’ needs. In this
          virtual roundtable hosted by <em>Advisor’s Edge</em> and <em>Investment Executive</em>, experts share the
          questions that can help you determine your clients’ values and objectives from RI/ESG
          investing. You’ll also hear about the factors that distinguish a truly committed and
          integrated RI/ESG process. Attendees will walk away with a list of questions to ask their
          clients as well as their product manufacturers. 
        </mj-text>

      </mj-column>

